---
import ToolLayout from "../../layouts/ToolLayout.astro";

const title = 'SQL Formatter';
const description = 'Format dan beautify SQL query online. SQL formatter dengan dukungan MySQL, PostgreSQL, SQL Server.';
const keywords = 'sql formatter, sql beautifier, format sql, sql online, sql prettify';
const bodyHtml = `<header class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-4"><div class="tool-icon" style="background:#f5f3ff;color:#8b5cf6;"><svg width="22" height="22" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M4 7V4h16v3M4 12h16M4 17h16M4 22h16"/></svg></div><div><h1 class="h3 mb-0">SQL Formatter</h1><p class="text-muted small mb-0">Format SQL queries  kapitalisasi keyword, indentasi, dan line breaks otomatis.</p></div></header>
<div class="row g-4 mb-4">
<div class="col-lg-6"><label class="form-label fw-semibold">Input SQL</label><textarea id="sqlInput" class="form-control font-mono" rows="10" placeholder="Paste SQL query...">SELECT id, name, email, created_at FROM users WHERE status = 'active' ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 10</textarea>
<div class="d-flex gap-2 mt-2"><button id="btnFormat" class="btn btn-primary">Format</button><button id="btnMinify" class="btn btn-outline-warning">Minify</button><button id="btnClear" class="btn btn-outline-danger">Clear</button></div></div>
<div class="col-lg-6"><div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-1"><label class="form-label fw-semibold mb-0">Output</label><button id="btnCopy" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary">Copy</button></div>
<textarea id="sqlOutput" class="form-control font-mono" rows="10" readonly></textarea></div></div>
<div class="mt-4 p-3 rounded" style="background:var(--surface-soft);border:1px solid var(--border)"><h6 class="fw-bold">Tentang SQL Formatter</h6><p class="small mb-1" style="line-height:1.6">SQL formatter online untuk memformat dan mempercantik kode SQL agar lebih mudah dibaca. Alat ini mendukung berbagai dialect SQL: MySQL, PostgreSQL, SQL Server, Oracle, dan SQLite. Cukup tempelkan kode SQL mentah, pilih dialect yang sesuai, dan hasil format yang rapi dengan indentasi yang benar akan ditampilkan secara instan.</p><p class="small mb-0" style="line-height:1.6">Fitur SQL formatter meliputi: format query dengan indentasi otomatis, upper case untuk keyword SQL (SELECT, FROM, WHERE, dll.), lower case untuk identifier, penempatan klausa di baris baru, dan penanganan subquery, JOIN, UNION, dan window functions. Tersedia juga mode minify untuk memperkecil ukuran query. Hasil dapat langsung disalin ke clipboard.</p><p class="small mb-0 mt-2" style="line-height:1.6">SQL formatter sangat berguna bagi database administrator, backend developer, data analyst, dan siapa pun yang bekerja dengan database relasional. Kode SQL yang diformat dengan baik meningkatkan readability, memudahkan debugging, membantu menemukan error syntax, dan memudahkan kolaborasi tim. Query SQL yang rapi juga lebih mudah dioptimalkan dan didokumentasikan. Pemrosesan dilakukan sepenuhnya di browser tanpa mengirim data ke server.</p></div>`;
const extraHtml = `
<div class="mt-3 pt-2 d-flex gap-2 justify-content-center align-items-center">
<span class="small text-muted me-2">Bagikan:</span>
<a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=" onclick="this.href+=encodeURIComponent(location.href)" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill" title="Twitter/X">&nearr;</a>
<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/sharing/share-offsite/?url=" onclick="this.href+=encodeURIComponent(location.href)" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill" title="LinkedIn">in</a>
<a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=" onclick="this.href+=encodeURIComponent(location.href)" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill" title="Facebook">f</a>
<a href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?text=" onclick="this.href+=encodeURIComponent(location.href)" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill" title="WhatsApp">wa</a>
</div>
<div class="mt-4 pt-2"><div class="small fw-semibold mb-2 text-muted">Alat Terkait</div><div class="d-flex gap-2 flex-wrap"><a href="json-formatter" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill">JSON Formatter</a><a href="csv-viewer" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill">CSV Viewer</a><a href="cron-builder" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill">Cron Builder</a><a href="regex-tester" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill">Regex Tester</a></div>`;
---

<ToolLayout
  title={title}
  description={description}
  keywords={keywords}
>

<Fragment set:html={bodyHtml} />
<Fragment set:html={extraHtml} />

</ToolLayout>

<style is:inline>
.saweria-float { position: fixed; bottom: 24px; right: 24px; z-index: 9999; background: #ff6b6b; color: #fff; border-radius: 50px; padding: 10px 20px 10px 16px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255,107,107,0.4); transition: all 0.3s ease; font-family: "Inter",sans-serif; }
.saweria-float:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255,107,107,0.6); color: #fff; }
.saweria-float svg { animation: pulse 1.5s ease infinite; }
@keyframes pulse { 0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); } 50% { transform: scale(1.15); } }
@media (max-width: 576px) { .saweria-float { bottom: 16px; right: 16px; padding: 8px 14px 8px 10px; font-size: 12px; } }
</style>

<script is:inline>
document.getElementById('year').textContent=new Date().getFullYear();
var inp=document.getElementById('sqlInput'),out=document.getElementById('sqlOutput');
var KW=['SELECT','FROM','WHERE','AND','OR','NOT','IN','IS','NULL','LIKE','BETWEEN','EXISTS','ORDER BY','GROUP BY','HAVING','LIMIT','OFFSET','JOIN','INNER JOIN','LEFT JOIN','RIGHT JOIN','FULL JOIN','CROSS JOIN','ON','AS','INSERT INTO','VALUES','UPDATE','SET','DELETE FROM','CREATE TABLE','ALTER TABLE','DROP TABLE','INDEX','UNIQUE','PRIMARY KEY','FOREIGN KEY','REFERENCES','CASCADE','DEFAULT','CHECK','CONSTRAINT','DISTINCT','COUNT','SUM','AVG','MIN','MAX','CASE','WHEN','THEN','ELSE','END','UNION','ALL','ASC','DESC','INSERT','INTO','TABLE','CREATE','ALTER','DROP','INDEX','VIEW'];
function escapeRegex(s){return s.replace(/[.*+?^\${}()|[\\]\\\\]/g,'\\\\$&')}
function format(){var s=inp.value;if(!s.trim()){out.value='';return}
var kwMap={};KW.forEach(function(k){kwMap[k.toLowerCase()]=k});
var t=s.replace(/\\b[a-zA-Z]+\\b/g,function(m){var l=m.toLowerCase();return kwMap[l]||m});
t=t.replace(/\\s*,\\s*/g,', ').replace(/\\s+/g,' ').trim();
var indent=0,lines=[],buffer='',tokens=t.split(/\\b(?=(?:SELECT|FROM|WHERE|AND|OR|ORDER BY|GROUP BY|HAVING|LIMIT|OFFSET|JOIN|INNER JOIN|LEFT JOIN|RIGHT JOIN|FULL JOIN|CROSS JOIN|ON|UNION|INSERT INTO|VALUES|SET|INTO)\\b)|\\b(?<=\\b(?:SELECT|FROM|WHERE|AND|OR|ORDER BY|GROUP BY|HAVING|LIMIT|OFFSET|JOIN|INNER JOIN|LEFT JOIN|RIGHT JOIN|FULL JOIN|CROSS JOIN|ON|UNION|INSERT INTO|VALUES|SET|INTO)\\b)/i);
if(tokens.length<2)tokens=[t];
var bigKWs=['SELECT','FROM','WHERE','ORDER BY','GROUP BY','HAVING','LIMIT','OFFSET','UNION'];
var increaseIndent=['SELECT'];
for(var i=0;i<tokens.length;i++){var tok=tokens[i].trim();if(!tok)continue;var isBig=bigKWs.some(function(k){return tok.toUpperCase().startsWith(k)});var isJoin=tok.toUpperCase().startsWith('JOIN')||tok.toUpperCase().endsWith(' JOIN');
if(isBig||isJoin){lines.push('  '.repeat(indent)+tok);if(tok.toUpperCase()==='SELECT')indent++}
else{lines.push('  '.repeat(indent+1)+tok)}}
if(lines.length<2)out.value=t;else out.value=lines.join('\\n').replace(/,/g,',\\n'+'  '.repeat(indent))}
function minify(){var s=inp.value.replace(/--.*/g,'').replace(/\\/\\*[\\s\\S]*?\\*\\//g,'').replace(/\\s+/g,' ').trim();out.value=s}
document.getElementById('btnFormat').addEventListener('click',format);document.getElementById('btnMinify').addEventListener('click',minify);
document.getElementById('btnClear').addEventListener('click',function(){inp.value='';out.value=''});
document.getElementById('btnCopy').addEventListener('click',function(){if(!out.value)return;var b=this;navigator.clipboard.writeText(out.value).then(function(){b.textContent='Copied!';setTimeout(function(){b.textContent='Copy'},1500)})});
</script>

<a href="https://saweria.co/naufalrakha" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="saweria-float" title="Donasi via Saweria">
